'''卡尔洪縣'''（{{lang en|'''Calhoun County'''}}）是[[美國|美國]][[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]南部的一個縣，面積1,638平方公里。根據[[美國2010年人口普查|2010年人口普查]]估計，本縣共有人口5,368人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://2010.census.gov/2010census/data/ |title=2010 census data |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2011-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706203009/http://2010.census.gov/2010census/data/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是州中人口最少的縣份。<ref name="NACO">{{cite web|url=http://www.naco.org/Template.cfm?Section=Find_a_County&Template=/cffiles/counties/state.cfm&state.cfm&statecode=AR|title=NACo - Find a county|author=National Association of Counties|accessdate=2007-04-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071025112518/http://www.naco.org/Template.cfm?Section=Find_a_County&Template=%2Fcffiles%2Fcounties%2Fstate.cfm&state.cfm&statecode=AR|archivedate=2007-10-25}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://argis.ualr.edu/2000Census_pdf/PopChar/00_pop_cty.pdf |title=Total Population; Arkansas by County |accessdate=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2012-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204211203/http://argis.ualr.edu/2000Census_pdf/PopChar/00_pop_cty.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>本縣縣治為[[汉普顿_(阿肯色州)|汉普顿]]。{{GR|6}}本縣是[[卡姆登_(阿肯色州)|卡姆登]][[卡姆登都會統計區|都會統計區]]的一部份。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.census.gov/popest/metro/tables/2009/CBSA-EST2009-01.csv | title = Table 1. Annual Estimates of the Population of Metropolitan and Micropolitan Statistical Areas: April 1, 2000 to July 1, 2009 (CBSA-EST2009-01) | format = [[comma-separated_values|CSV]] | work = 2009 Population Estimates | publisher = [[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]], Population Division | date = 2010-03-23 | accessdate = 2010-03-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110604062237/http://www.census.gov/popest/metro/tables/2009/CBSA-EST2009-01.csv | archive-date = 2011-06-04 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

本縣於1850年12月6日成立，是州中第55個成立的縣份。縣名紀念曾任兩屆[[美國副總統|副總統]]的[[約翰·C·卡爾霍恩|約翰·C·卡爾霍恩]]。{{GR|3}}

